---
title: Caesar Salad with Honey Butter Cornbread | 2 Servings
description: Making a salad is easy, but making a good salad can take work—until now. This crunchy and refreshing mix is ready in minutes and packed with crisp romaine lettuce, Parmesan cheese, and garlic and cheese croutons. Take this salad to the next level by tossing everything in a deliciously creamy Caesar dressing. We made it easy to turn these greens into a full meal with a side of sweet and fluffy cornbread. Yum!

